00:01:49.390 --> 00:01:51.410
then I look it up and this usually happens.

00:01:51.410 --> 00:01:52.650
If I'm reading through something,

00:01:52.650 --> 00:01:54.480
I decide to skip a word and keep reading.

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:58.930
